Name: Space FURY - The Phantom Menace
About the game: You are buying the finished game. All future upgrades will be free of charge. An old-school space shooter in 3D. Collect 'PowerUp' its a main resource for you. It is both an improvement to your main weapon and armor. Never take damage from enemies! Taking damage will weaken your main weapon and make it even harder for you! Your equipment from the previous episode is saved for the next one. Keep a close eye on your resources, or you will have to replay the previous episode. To get 5 stars on all episodes you need to show a masterful game!
